trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument"></xref> objects that are stored as key/value pairs.
trans-unit.target: 代表集合<xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.RemoteArgument"></xref>物件會儲存為索引鍵/值組。

trans-unit.source: Each element in an IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract is a key/value pair that is stored in a <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry> object.
trans-unit.target: IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract 中的每個項目是儲存在索引鍵/值組<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry>物件。</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.RemoteArgumentDictionaryEntry>

trans-unit.source: Each key/value pair must have a unique key.
trans-unit.target: 每個索引鍵/值組必須具有唯一索引鍵。

trans-unit.source: The IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract interface enables the contained keys and values to be enumerated, but it does not imply any particular sort order.
trans-unit.target: IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract 介面，讓包含索引鍵和要列舉的值，但它並不代表任何特定排序順序。
